title: Free Agent Matches Made in Fantasy Heaven | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We start with a quick discussion about some NFL contract misconceptions before taking a look at the upcoming free agency free-for-all through a fantasy lens, examining the big names set to potentially join new teams—and how that could affect the fantasy landscape—and also dole out some of our favorite fantasy matches made in heaven.
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
